I'm the executive producer of this show.

43
00:02:39,983 --> 00:02:41,582
I absolutely won't allow it to fail.

44
00:02:41,983 --> 00:02:43,503
I don't allow my show

45
00:02:43,622 --> 00:02:44,663
to be interfered with.

46
