181
00:08:51,943 --> 00:08:54,022
I was so nervous.

182
00:08:54,902 --> 00:08:55,502
Is that so?

183
00:08:56,142 --> 00:08:57,463
Someone seems to have said
that once she

184
00:08:57,943 --> 00:08:58,703
had a breakdown,

185
00:08:58,782 --> 00:09:00,382
