187
00:09:03,382 --> 00:09:04,103
I'll give you a pass.

188
00:09:04,262 --> 00:09:05,262
Say whatever you want.

189
00:09:12,022 --> 00:09:12,902
Hello, Mr. Qin.

190
00:09:13,183 --> 00:09:13,902
Tao.

191
00:09:15,502 --> 00:09:16,943
