192
00:09:17,583 --> 00:09:18,303
No.

193
00:09:18,703 --> 00:09:20,382
I came with my dad.

194
00:09:20,943 --> 00:09:21,542
Your father?

195
00:09:21,823 --> 00:09:23,862
I hear he's not feeling well
with his heart

196
00:09:23,983 --> 00:09:25,502
