204
00:09:41,103 --> 00:09:42,583
I want you to cure my dad.

205
00:09:42,742 --> 00:09:44,583
I want you to do it.

206
00:09:44,703 --> 00:09:45,502
Tao,

207
00:09:45,502 --> 00:09:46,423
we should go home.

208
00:09:47,103 --> 00:09:47,823
Yes.

209
00:10:01,902 --> 00:10:03,183
