instantly captured on camera♪

235
00:11:17,382 --> 00:11:18,223
Yes, look here.

236
00:11:18,303 --> 00:11:20,022
I want the feeling of light coming in.

237
00:11:21,103 --> 00:11:22,662
Remember the wound
can't touch the water.

238
00:11:23,862 --> 00:11:25,423
