242
00:11:38,476 --> 00:11:42,120
♪Whether it's sunny or rainy,
I'm not in a rush♪

243
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:44,296
♪My heart's racing♪

244
00:11:44,296 --> 00:11:45,782
♪With you around, I have expectations♪

245
00:11:45,782 --> 00:11:47,223
