254
00:12:07,542 --> 00:12:08,343
Look at that star.

255
00:12:08,343 --> 00:12:09,183
It's so beautiful.

256
00:12:22,943 --> 00:12:23,983
Everyone, perk up.

257
00:12:24,183 --> 00:12:25,463
It is the last day of the filming

258
00:12:25,502 --> 00:12:27,542
of the glass house.

259
00:12:28,583 --> 00:12:29,943
